    bbox:
      x: 10
      y: 10
      w: 940
      h: 620
    layout: "manual"

    purpose: "Primary molecular visualization"
    nodes:
      - id: rubisco
        label: "RuBisCO"
        shape: "oval"
        color: "lightblue"

        label: "CO2"
        shape: "rectangle"
        color: "gray"
      - id: rubp
        label: "RuBP"
        shape: "rectangle"
        color: "lightgreen"
      - id: glucose
        label: "Glucose"
        shape: "rectangle"
        color: "lightyellow"
    edges:
      - src: co2
        dst: rubp
        label: "attaches"
      - src: rubp
        dst: rubisco
        label: "processed by"
      - src: rubisco
        dst: glucose
        label: "produces"
